# lib @openhint/transpiler

Library provides the programmatic API for the HINT ecosystem. It handles file pre-processing, variable resolution, and markdown compilation.

The parser and compiler honor the root `hint.yml` or `hint.yaml` `ignore` array for every target, cascaded HINT file, compile-time include, and run-time read reference.

# dependencies

Development:

- {PresetTypescript}
- {PresetEslint}
- vite
- node
- typescript
